# 8. 消えたがってるくせに

???: Miku, why are there people here?
Miku: .....
Mizuki: Huh? Yuki? Now that you mention it, it does sound like her.
Ena: But is this really Yuki? She seems completely different from when we talk on Nightcord.
Kanade: Yuki...
???: K?
Kanade: Yeah, that's right.
Ena: It really is Yuki...
???: And you two must be Enanan and Amia.
Mizuki: I'm so glad you're okay, Yuki! We were getting worried after not hearing from you for so long.
Mizuki: Have you been here the whole time? Did you get stuck here because you couldn't find a way to get back?
???: .....
Mizuki: What's wrong? Yuki, are you okay? Are you hungry from not having eaten since you got here or something?
???: Annoying...
Mizuki: Huh?
???: Stay out of my world and leave me alone.
Ena: What is that supposed to mean? Are you saying you don't want to go home?
???: I just said that.
???: I want to be left alone here.
Kanade: Alone? That's...
Ena: What's going on here?
Mizuki: Um... Then, does that mean you don't want to keep making songs with us?
???: That's right. How many times do I have to say it?
Kanade: .....
Mizuki: Yeah, but this kinda feels a bit sudden, you know? Look, even Kanade is surprised. Right, Kanade?
Kanade: Yuki...
???: What?
Kanade: Does that mean you just want to make songs by yourself from now on as OWN?
Ena: What? OWN? You mean... What?
Kanade: Yuki is OWN.
Mizuki: What? Yuki is OWN? What are you talking about?!
???: Where's your proof?
Kanade: I have none, but I can tell. The songs may be completely different than the ones we make as N25, but I'm sure of it.
Kanade: Isn't that right, Yuki?
???: .....
???: Yeah, that's right. I'm OWN.
Mizuki: S-Seriously?
Ena: Are you really OWN?
???: That's what I said.
Ena: What? So that means the entire time Amia and I were talking about OWN the other day...
Ena: Why didn't you say anything?
???: I didn't see any reason to tell you, so I didn't.
???: I've never spoken to you as anyone other than Yuki, after all.
Ena: Huh?
Ena: What's that supposed to mean?!
Ena: So what was going through your head while I went off about how amazing you were without even knowing the truth? Were you just having a laugh at my expense?!
Mizuki: C-Calm down, Enanan! Can we at least talk about this a little more, Yuki?
Mizuki: Even if you are OWN, do you really have to stop being part of N25? This is all way too sudden...
???: There's no reason for me to remain part of N25.
Mizuki: Uh... What?
???: Being in N25 wasn't enough.
Kanade: Enough for what?
???: .....
???: K, the first time I heard your songs, I felt like they had saved me. A little bit.
???: So I thought being near you might be enough to help me find what I was looking for.
???: But it wasn't enough. I wasn't able to find anything.
Kanade: Oh...
[Yuki]: <I felt like your song saved me.>
Kanade: So...I wasn't able to save you...?
???: And if being around you won't help me find what I'm looking for, then I'll just have to do it on my own.
???: Miku, I have nothing else to say to these people. Get them out of here.
Miku: I see.
Miku: Can you really find what you're looking for on your own?
???: .....
???: If you say there's still a possibility I can find myself, then I will give up everything to do so.
???: That is the only option left. But if I can't find myself even then...then I'll just have to disappear.
Miku: .....
Ena: What the heck are you even talking about?! Being saved?! Disappear?! What's wrong with you?!
Mizuki: Come on, let's talk about this. You're acting strange, Yuki.
???: Strange? If I'm strange, then so are all of you.
???: Be honest, K, Enanan, Amia... You all want to disappear more than anyone.
Kanade & Ena: !!
Mizuki: .....
???: And yet you call me strange?
Mizuki: Seriously, what's gotten into you, Yuki? What do you mean I want to disappear? I love my life, so why would I think that?
???: You don't have to do this anymore.
???: Amia, you always act like you're having fun, but deep down you know exactly what I'm talking about, don't you?
Mizuki: ..... Oh, really?
???: Anyway, I'm tired of this.
???: Miku. I don't want these people in my world.
Miku: Okay.
Ena: Huh? Miku! H-Hold on!
Mizuki: What? When Miku touched her, she just disappeared!
Miku: Now, you.
Mizuki: Ah!
Kanade: Mizuki!
Miku: And you, too...
Kanade: Wait!
Miku: Goodbye...
Miku: But please...find a way to save Mafuyu.
